title: Spacious 1BR - Downtown Views - Balcony - Ideal Location
posting_body: ['Borealis is a walkable, bikeable retreat in the vibrant North Loop neighborhood.', 'Featuring modern, upgraded interiors, beautiful (and functional!)', 'floor plans, and superior customer service, Borealis has received rave reviews from happy residents since opening its doors in March 2018.', 'Visit our Google page or read more about the building here: <URL>', '#302 -- Plan M', 'Plan M is a one bed, one bath layout available on the 3rd floor with downtown views!', 'This home features a balcony, built-in desk nook, a black granite kitchen island and polished concrete flooring.', ' Natural light pours through the floor to ceiling windows.', ' This is the ideal apartment for those who are looking for a spacious one-bedroom with chic finishes, great design, stunning amenities and a convenient location!', ' (Photos of exact unit.)', 'For info on amenities and to apply: <URL>', 'Prices subject to change.', 'Minneapolis -- Mpls -- North Loop -- Warehouse District -- NE -- Northeast -- U of M -- Boutique -- Luxury -- Scandinavian -- Mid-Century Modern -- Bike Friendly -- Pet, Dog, Cat Friendly -- Green Living -- Sustainable -- Electric Car Charging -- New Construction']
